sub_title: Owner of tour operator Paladares Travel. The company offers exclusive food & wine tours with a sense of place in Portugal and Spain.
summary:
I am the owner of Paladares Travel, a tour operator / travel agency. The company offers exclusive food & wine holidays / tours in Portugal and Spain. 
Paladares Travel was set up in 2005.
 
Prior to 2005 I spent my career working as an international banker, managing relationships with banks, broker/dealers, asset managers, other financial institutions and companies.   
  
As a banker I worked in investment banking in London, and in commercial banking while based in Amsterdam.

It was during my time working in London, that I was inspired to develop my passion for travel, food & wine and create a gastronomic travel company.

Specialties: Marketing and sales strategies 
Strategic planning and implementation
Tourism
Food & wine
Travel
